    <!-- About us -->
    <section id="About">
        <h2 class="text-center pt-4 mt-5">About Us</h2>
            <div class="col-10 offset-1">
                    <p class="text-justify">The Prime Minister's Special Scholarship Scheme (PMSSS) is a scholarship scheme that was launched by the Ministry of Human Resource Development, Government of India, to provide financial aid to students from Jammu and Kashmir and Ladakh to pursue higher education in colleges and universities across the country. The scheme was launched in 2011 and has been implemented by the All India Council for Technical Education (AICTE).</p>
                    <p class="text-justify">The Prime Minister's Special Scholarship Scheme (PMSSS) aims to provide financial support to students from all across India. Through this portal, students can submit their documents, track their scholarship status, and receive timely payments. Our system ensures that the entire process is paperless, efficient, and secure.</p>
            </div>
    </section>

